    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Beyond The Darkness》是一段会让你沉浸在童年梦魇的黑暗故事，即使你试图忘掉也逃不了。帮助小女孩米莉对抗潜伏在黑暗中的惊恐，并找回她失散已久的家人。你将发现自己置身在满载回忆的古怪世界，空间因惊恐及绝望而扭曲，而你唯一的武器便是手中那盏小灯的光线…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/b068c3f6b929d5833827977119c892be.poster.avif?t=1731848932\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/b068c3f6b929d5833827977119c892be.webm?t=1731848932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你唯一的防御机制，就是光线。可别让米莉的灯灭掉了；用灯来照亮道路、解开谜题，并抵御可怕的生物。但记住啦，灯火并非永无止境；若消耗得太快，就有可能遭黑暗永久吞噬！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/da52b10999aec77f948036d8f2adc6c6.poster.avif?t=1731848932\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/da52b10999aec77f948036d8f2adc6c6.webm?t=1731848932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Beyond The Darkness》中，真正的怪物守株待兔，渴望摧毁任何一丝希望，并将米莉拉进绝望的深渊。每只怪物都是童年恐惧的化身，准备在你不经意时发动攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/a064a6a76ff6a3400684a43aa24f21dc.poster.avif?t=1731848932\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/a064a6a76ff6a3400684a43aa24f21dc.webm?t=1731848932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上穿梭回忆交织的危险旅程。找出可建构事件轨迹的重要元素并查明真相，但务必记得你看到的世界眼见不能为凭，在看不到的深处，潜伏着真正的梦魇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/e90d58c12ec92b5c27e7ffdf4b3cad2d.poster.avif?t=1731848932\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728610/extras/e90d58c12ec92b5c27e7ffdf4b3cad2d.webm?t=1731848932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候，回忆错纵盘缠，而答案埋藏在最深刻之处。帮助米莉破解遇到的重重难关。找出正确的解法可能相当艰巨，尤其你只是个胆战心惊的小孩。错误可是要付出高昂的代价……只要一个致命的错误，就足以让希望之光永久抹灭。可别让光芒熄灭了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
